Author: 50MHz#3277
Content: I’m sure all of you guys already know this, but let me tell you about my scam experience on eBay. First off never send any crypto to eBay sellers! I’m sitting chomping at the bits to get a Z11 because I want to my mining op to grow, so I venture over to eBay because all z11’s are sold out. I see this ad and buy the machine because this guy has great reviews but he wants to be paid in crypto, at first I find it strange but then again I have bought so many machines from bitmain that it doesn’t seem that odd. Long story short this guy says the listing was never his and basically I sent my btc to a scammer address either it be him or someone that “hacked” his eBay account. So let me lose out on money so you don’t! Don’t send crypto to eBay sellers, bad idea friends!
